## Description {#details}

This file contains constants used for implementing Dwarf debug support.

For details on the Dwarf specfication see the latest DWARF Debugging Information Format standard document on <a href="http://www.dwarfstd.org">http://www.dwarfstd.org</a>. This file often includes support for non-released standard features.
